      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>&gt;@Compendium[sfrpg.class-features.jNB7NzoNZ64YcvK8]{Apocalypse}</p>\n<p>Each foe within 30 feet takes damage equal to your vanguard level and is subject to an additional effect (Fortitude negates). Roll 1d6 for each affected foe, using the result to determine the damage type and effect.</p>\n<p><em>Improved: </em>The damage increases to twice your vanguard level. You can roll 1d6 twice for each affected foe, choosing one of the two results to apply.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<table style=\"height: 119px; width: 64.0221%; border-style: solid;\" border=\"1\">\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height: 17px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 5.5102%; height: 17px;\"><strong>D6</strong></td>\n<td style=\"width: 94.4898%; height: 17px;\"><strong>Damage &amp; Effect</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 17px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 5.5102%; height: 17px;\">1</td>\n<td style=\"width: 94.4898%; height: 17px;\">Acid damage and entangled for 1 round.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 17px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 5.5102%; height: 17px;\">2</td>\n<td style=\"width: 94.4898%; height: 17px;\">Bludgeoning damage and knocked prone.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 17px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 5.5102%; height: 17px;\">3</td>\n<td style=\"width: 94.4898%; height: 17px;\">Cold damage and fatigued for 1 round.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 17px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 5.5102%; height: 17px;\">4</td>\n<td style=\"width: 94.4898%; height: 17px;\">Electric damage and staggered for 1 round.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 17px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 5.5102%; height: 17px;\">5</td>\n<td style=\"width: 94.4898%; height: 17px;\">Fire damage and burning 1d6 per 4 vanguard levels.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 17px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 5.5102%; height: 17px;\">6</td>\n<td style=\"width: 94.4898%; height: 17px;\">Sonic damage and sickened for 1 round.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>"
